{"tid":2342010,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"電影版《鬼滅之刃》終破《千與千尋》紀錄登日本史上票房冠軍","createTime":"2020-12-26T19:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T20:40:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94d332e6f76e9f5e7694c5a8b19e997e2d467856","tid":2342010,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T19:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WrgPgX3ce_PlVhQEY8-fAj5Uhp0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WBNCDBDW4RCPXF4RAAS7HPC7TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWrgPgX3ce_PlVhQEY8-fAj5Uhp0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWBNCDBDW4RCPXF4RAAS7HPC7TY.jpg&h=b1acc9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本動漫歌姬LiSA昨晚有份演出的朝日電視台節目《Music Station Ultra Super Live 2020》，由下午5點起播足六小時，共66組歌手及組合輪流表演，LiSA獻唱《鬼滅之刃》了兩首主題曲《紅蓮華》和《炎》，其間更大玩「炎柱」視覺效果，配合《炎》一曲以最新CG&middot;AR技術呈現出人氣角色煉獄杏壽郎的世界觀，畫面壯觀。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》在日本10月開畫後屢破紀錄。電影在當地上映72天，總票房累積317.2億日圓（約23.73億港元），終打破動畫大師宮崎駿2001年名作《千與千尋》創下的316.8億日圓（約23.70億港元），成為日本的史上票房冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AlHcxU40Z2WOpTIgcyw4Hj7ydbw=/802x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ONFME3FT45CLPPS3RELKLPU6RM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAlHcxU40Z2WOpTIgcyw4Hj7ydbw%3D%2F802x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FONFME3FT45CLPPS3RELKLPU6RM.jpg&h=d45c460e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7RfiZcbW47qWAkAOgSkVxFPJUfg=/802x1130/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7HBTXTFLCNHW5J5AJLFYLOV4CE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7RfiZcbW